## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not capture all regional or emerging trends in healthcare delivery. Additionally, the rapidly changing nature of the healthcare industry means that new forces may emerge that are not covered in this report. The reliance on secondary sources also means that some nuances of the primary data may be lost.